com.bulletphysics.collision.dispatch

Class DefaultCollisionConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bulletphysics.collision.dispatch.CollisionConfiguration
      • com.bulletphysics.collision.dispatch.DefaultCollisionConfiguration

  • public class DefaultCollisionConfiguration
extends CollisionConfiguration
    Default implementation of CollisionConfiguration. Provides all core collision algorithms. Some extra algorithms (like GImpact) must be registered manually by calling appropriate register method.
